#CHIP DMG
#CLOCK 4194304

; DMG (Game Boy) APU - Pulse Channels Test
;
; Tests CH1 and CH2 (square wave pulse channels).
; Each channel is independently addressable with note-on/off.

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; CH1 pulse: simple melody
c4 d4 e4 f4

g4 a4 b4 c5

; CH2 pulse: harmony a third below
e4 f4 g4 a4

; Both channels together
c4 & e4

r2

#END
